{"tid":1035570,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人可以屌醒我","createTime":"2019-02-24T16:27:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-03T04:21:16.000Z","uid":844,"like":2,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"36e845e3b5d8bba61b5d88418992c792084fe4c3","tid":1035570,"uid":844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T16:27:44.000Z","msg":"12月頭條女話唔適合 做番朋友  因為我成日都不滿佢同幾個男仔fd成日好close 好曖昧咁 成日發佢脾氣<br />\n之後都有keep住曖昧 佢都會主動打比我 搵我<br />\n到聖誕諗住比機會我一齊番 但第日因為同一件事又發脾氣<br />\n 佢就話諗得好清楚都係唔適合<br />\n之後今次就好冷淡 完全唔理我<br />\n 呢段時間我成日係咁鬧佢 話佢同第個男仔有野<br />\n我同佢同事黎 日日睇住佢同其他男仔玩得好開心好曖昧 我又忍唔住好嬲 好想鬧佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢今次咁耐真係完全理都無理過我<br />\n返工要對住佢見住佢同其他仔咁開心 真係好痛苦<br />\n我就自己on99"},{"pid":"3b83156a3761000a34e5b6118593267bce6e0e6e","tid":1035570,"uid":112390,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T16:28:51.000Z","msg":"臭雞<br />\n咁會唔會好d？"},{"pid":"2a1826cc125d1dcce7ade8b6958a4aaab15f700c","tid":1035570,"uid":40226,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T16:29:55.000Z","msg":"垃撚圾"},{"pid":"81585c19a26f636aba0d3b690f759d52f6fd9318","tid":1035570,"uid":844,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T16:31:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a89ee9bad68cba378fafb872395fc2e55a53968","tid":1035570,"uid":157451,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T16:31:14.000Z","msg":"吓 條女問題啦 拍得拖要保守d<br />\n同其他異性保持適當距離 唔係好正常咩"},{"pid":"13e6fea32e12fa10a2d59da217e9e978ed255a01","tid":1035570,"uid":202488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T16:31:21.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"b0cbc3946c1f18d8dbcf77b6419830c686526fb4","tid":1035570,"uid":93043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,